      "text": "――という訳で、あの人気の女性誌から遙子さんに\nグラビアとインタビューのオファーがきたんです",
      "startTime": 4.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "凄い！　私、この雑誌いつも買ってるのよ！",
      "startTime": 7.2527433396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "大人可愛い系のファッションスナップとか\n毎月のインタビューや特集も充実してるの",
      "startTime": 15.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "特に、今活躍するタレントさんやアイドルの\nグラビアとインタビューが凄く面白いんだから！",
      "startTime": 23.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、活躍している人達って\nプライベートも素敵なのよね。憧れちゃうわ",
      "startTime": 29.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "愛読していたんですね\n遙子さんにとって、いい仕事になりそうで良かったです",
      "startTime": 36.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "後は『デンジャラスピロ美の占いコーナー』も好きね\n名言が多くて、切り抜いてファイリングしているわ",
      "startTime": 44.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "う、占いコーナーの切り抜き……\n遙子さん、そんな趣味を隠し持っていたんですね",
      "startTime": 52.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_10_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "何よその反応～。『地味な趣味』とか思ったんでしょ\nこれでも、トークのネタになるんだからね？",
      "startTime": 63.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
